About the game:

Continue the feeding frenzy action in this wild underwater mystery! As a small fish you'll need to stay afloat by dodging the big ones that are out to gobble you up. Eat your own way up the food chain in 2 exciting modes while discovering beautiful underwater environments and fabulous new fish. The feeding is more frenzied than ever!
